                    @{"             iNSTALL              " link 2}


 Unpack The Archive Into Your Doors Directory. Alter The File Called
 sUPER_lOG.bbs And Put Your BBS Name As The Text, Or Watever. Alter The
 Main Screen If You Wish, But Keeping In Mind That The Text Stays In The
 Same Position, Etc. Finally Execute The Door Via A Menu Or Via Intro
 During Login! I Think That's About It, I think!? ;-)

